{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The kingdom of Faunis is under siege, and only your team of makeshift builders can reclaim it! However, the task is easier said than done as waves of enemies will be set to ruin your efforts.\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228720/extras/hbc_Eng.png?t=1734629011\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resource blocks, strategically construct barricades to disrupt enemy paths, and craft defensive mechanisms to fortify your base.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228720/extras/hbc.gif?t=1734629011\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228720/extras/plans_eng.png?t=1734629011\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle alongside your custom-built defenses! Use blocks, toss enemies, and even launch your friends to fend off the onslaught in fast-paced, physics-based combat.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228720/extras/plans.gif?t=1734629011\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228720/extras/stack_eng.png?t=1734629011\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stack resource blocks and defenses to amplify their power. Higher stacks mean tougher barricades and stronger turrets\u2014it's all about strategic placement and maximizing your fortifications.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228720/extras/stack.gif?t=1734629011\" />\u00a0